{"tid":132934,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"lbj既生涯就好比一個打工仔","createTime":"2017-02-24T07:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T06:31:43.000Z","uid":22580,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d68066cfbfeda7ceceee950e64364125776b3313","tid":132934,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"一畢業就入左家鄉間細公司度做 <br />\n做左幾年就以一人之力幫間細公司打入國際市場 <br />\n仲令呢間公司起死回身, 成為全球焦點, 搵左好多錢 <br />\n<br />\n但係呢間公司永遠都比唔到好既同事佢夾 資金又冇 <br />\n咩都係佢一個做晒 仲要年年做完都係得條毛 <br />\n但係佢唔介意 照樣為呢間公司打拼足7-8年 <br />\n<br />\n最後有前輩(KG)提醒佢唔好再浪費光陰 <br />\n叫佢出去大公司學多d野 <br />\n所以佢去左好朋友間公司到做 <br />\n仲因為個人能力係果間大公司做埋大佬 <br />\n當中佢學到好多野 拎左好多獎 <br />\n<br />\n之後佢覺得係大公司得到既野巳經足夠 <br />\n係時候返去為家鄉間細公司拼博 <br />\n最後成功令家鄉間細公司變成 top 1<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6127e5f8c093c44762e927cb527458168e6442","tid":132934,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"細公司d人都原諒晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88155939a5a98ef80a045e1579ac8baab69c35b1","tid":132934,"uid":6026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細公司d人都原諒晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再撚感動既係返去細公司打工，有支持者著返當日出走果時燒穿哂既衫為lbj打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7240f53e116c170088d87572f84c786b5cf8f270","tid":132934,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"違背向新公司嘅口頭承諾驚慌著草，<br />\n多次詐騙後表示自己從不詐騙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d48032f7534825437b7de946f1843db3de2a38f","tid":132934,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>違背向新公司嘅口頭承諾驚慌著草，<br />\n多次詐騙後表示自己從不詐騙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫新公司拎左兩年全球最佳公司"},{"pid":"1b5664c96569aa1c4a49cac4a1ff067bac2e88b8","tid":132934,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7777e6ed4183a7c0b81ba4af3823e9f64b39dfd7","tid":132934,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"一唔開冷氣就即刻早退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f3689afdbbde52aba7680eb8685ad5aff2d0e3","tid":132934,"uid":49532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"公司 this is for you!"},{"pid":"e56dd186b6b2f4eac5d7110b65daf3e18bea7237","tid":132934,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一唔開冷氣就即刻早退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b100e2edad831f2382eec94a65e48d301dc24b","tid":132934,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一唔開冷氣就即刻早退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186764d3a968984f